## ubuntu-desktop 20.04 基础版本

```text

cd docker-ubuntu-desktop
./docker_build.sh 20.04
```

## verdi 容器

<font size=15 color="red"> --mac-address=ae:ac:ae:71:1c:2d </font>要和后面加密配合使用

```text
docker run -d --restart=on-failure \
--name rocktan001-desktop-2004 \
-h rocktan001 \
--device /dev/fuse --cap-add=SYS_PTRACE --cap-add SYS_ADMIN \
--shm-size=1024m \
-v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix:rw \
-v /media/disk1/:/media/disk1/ \
-p 10059:10059 \
-p 14000:4000 \
-e ROOT_PWD=root \
-e SSH_PORT=10059 \
-e YSEMI_USER=Y10059 \
--mac-address=ae:ac:ae:71:1c:2d \
rocktan001/ubuntu-desktop:20.04
```

## vcs 环境安装

### /bin/sh illegal option -h

![avator][2]

[2]:data:image/png;base64,

```text
echo "dash dash/sh boolean false" | debconf-set-selections
dpkg-reconfigure dash

sudo dpkg-reconfigure dash # no
```

![avator][3]

[3]:data:image/png;base64,

### dc: command not found

```text
sudo apt-get install dc
```

### bash: ./lmgrd: No such file or directory

```text
sudo apt-get install lsb
```

### no such file :/usr/tmp/.flexlm
```text
sudo mkdir -p /usr/tmp/.flexlm
```

### libnuma.so.1:
```text
sudo apt-get install numactl
```

### libpng12.so.0
```text
cp /media/disk1/synopsys/patch/libpng12.so.0/libpng12.so.0 /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/
```
